	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">qtoyoda wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Nes mods guy, do you have to know code to do some siimple mods on nes games ? and if you mod games you can make them into .ips files correct?</div>
<br />
<br />You don't actually have to know 6502 asm to modify NES games. To do some of the more hardcore modding a bit more extensive knowledge is required.
<br />
<br />Also, I have no clue what an '.ips' file is.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
